edu.utah.cdmcc.reports
Class HTMLReportGenerator

java.lang.Object
  edu.utah.cdmcc.reports.HTMLReportGenerator

public class HTMLReportGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates creation of an HTML report in a browser shell. Users need to instantiate the class and call createHTMLReport with a valid report design. The report is displayed in a browser.

Author:
J. Michael Dean, M.D., M.B.A.
